SENATE CHAMBER
STATE OF OKLAHOMA DISPOSITION
FLOOR AMENDMENT No. ________
COMMITTEE AMENDMENT
(Date)
I move to amend Senate Bill No. 1327 on Page 2, Line 5 ½, by inserting a new subsection B to read
as follows, by relettering subsequent subsections, and by amending the title to conform:
“B. Each appointed member of the Commission shall demonstrate experience in one or more
of the following fields directly related to economic growth and tourism development:
1. Hospitality management;
2. Venue management;
3. Tourism promotion;
4. Real estate development;
5. Outdoor recreation;
6. Marketing and branding; and
7. Financial operations.”
